{"id": "28109", "revid": "10132", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28109", "title": "Leon Bat\u00ecsta Alberti", "text": "Leon Batt\u00ecsta Alberti (Zena, 14 frev\u00e2 1404-Romma, 25 arv\u00ee 1472) o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to 'n archit\u00e9tto, 'no scrit\u00f4, in matem\u00e0tico, 'n uman\u00ecsta, in critt\u00f2grafo, in lengo\u00ecsta, in fil\u00f2zofo, in muxic\u00ecsta e 'n archi\u00f2logo de sch\u00eaua italiann-a.\nV\u00ectta.\nScr\u00eeti.\n\u2022 \"Apologi centum\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Cena familiaris\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De amore\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De equo animante\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De Iciarchia\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De componendis cifris\" \u00f2 \"De cifris\", 1466 (critograf\u00eea)&lt;br&gt; \n\u2022 \"Deiphira\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De pictura\", in itali\u00e0n, 1435, co d\u00e9dica a F\u00e9ipo Brunelleschi, p\u00f6i in lat\u00ecn.&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Porcaria coniuratio\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De re aedificatoria\", 1450&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De statua\", 1462&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Descriptio urbis Romae\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Ecatomphile\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Elementa picturae\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Epistola consolatoria\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Grammatica della lingua toscana\", 1438-1441&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Intercoenales\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"De familia libri IV\", 1433-1437 (di\u00e0loghi)&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Ex ludis rerum mathematicorum\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Momus\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Philodoxeos fabula\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Profugiorum ab \u00e6rumna libri III\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Sentenze pitagoriche\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Sophrona\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Theogenius\"&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Villa\"&lt;br&gt;\nManoscr\u00eeti.\n\u2022 \"Liber de iure, scriptus Bononiae anno 1437\", Mil\u00e0n, Bibliot\u00eaca Ambrosian-a, ms. I 193 inf., ff. 1v-13r.&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Trivia senatoria\", Mil\u00e0n, Bibliot\u00eaca Ambrosiann-a, ms. I 193 inf., ff. 13v-19v.&lt;br&gt;\n\u2022 \"Philodoxeos Fabula\", Modena, Bibliot\u00eaca Estense, ms. alfa.o.07.09.&lt;br&gt;"}
