{"id": "28176", "revid": "12552", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28176", "title": "Turta de s\u00fccca d\u00fbse", "text": "A turta de s\u00fccca d\u00fbse a l'\u00e8 'na turta tipica prie\u1e61e e da va\u00e2 du Ma\u00e9mua prepa\u00e2 inte feste de l'aut\u00fcnnu (da T\u00fctti i S\u00e0nti fin a cuelle de Den\u00e2), a se tr\u00f6va asc\u00ec a L\u00f6a, dunde a l'\u00e8 tipica du24 de dixenbre. Segundu e leg\u00e9nde luc\u00e0li a l'\u00e8 ina ris\u00e8tta antich\u00ecscima, ch'a v\u00e9gne prepa\u00e2 dau XVII seculu.\nIngredienti pe 6/8 pers\u00f9ne.\nA sfoglia.\n\u2022 200gr de fa\u00eena (de lungu a l'\u00e8 dev\u00f6\u00e2 cuella integr\u00e2le)\n\u2022 \u00eagua (ad \u00f6ggiu, cuanta a ne b\u00e0sta)\n\u2022 \u00f6iu de o\u00eeva (cuantu ne basta)\nU c\u00ecn.\n\u2022 1,5 kg de s\u00fccca giana\n\u2022 in \u00f6vu\n\u2022 in c\u00fcgi\u00e2 de fa\u00eena de c\u00eaxi\n\u2022 50 gr de pign\u00f6i\n\u2022 50 gr de \u00fcgh\u00e9tta\n\u2022 3 c\u00fcgi\u00ea de Marsala\n\u2022 100 gr de s\u00fcc\u00e2 semu\u00e2\nPreparasi\u00f9n.\nP\u00e9 cumens\u00e0 bez\u00f6gna inbast\u00ee i ingredienti p\u00e9 a sfoglia, inpast\u00e0nduli ass\u00e8mme fin a cuande u nu se f\u00f9rma in inpastu m\u00f2rbidu. Da chi u b\u00e0sta pass\u00e0lu in t'ina p\u00fccag\u00e9tta, p\u00e9 f\u00e2lu ripu\u1e61\u00e2.\nLasc\u00ea a s\u00fccca in sce in f\u00f6iu de l\u00e0tta e met\u00eela intu f\u00f9rnu a 200 gr\u00e0ddi p\u00e9 cu\u1e61ai m\u00e8\u1e61\u1e61'\u00f9a o in \u00f9a, vistu che u tenpu u dip\u00e9nde dae dimensci\u00f9i de sta ch\u00ec. Lev\u00ea i semmi e a sc\u00fcrsa.\nIntu mentre and\u00e0i a sciacc\u00e2 cun a furs\u00eena a purpe da s\u00fccca, da inse\u00ec asc\u00ec l'\u00fcghetta intu Marsala, doppu av\u00e9la lav\u00e2.\nAnd\u00e0i poi a mescci\u00e2 au Mars\u00e0la l'\u00f6vu, a s\u00fcc\u00e2, a fa\u00eena de c\u00e9xi e asc\u00ec i pign\u00f6i, cun in c\u00fcgi\u00e2. Divid\u00e9i p\u00f2i a sfoglia in d\u00f9i furme re\u00f9nde, inse\u00ec inte 'na teja a sfoglia e poi asc\u00ec l'inpastu. Ser\u00ea i b\u00f9rdi ben e met\u00eei t\u00fcttu a c\u00f6xe intu furnu, fin a cuande u cu\u00fb da cr\u00f2sta u nu u l'\u00e8 bellu du\u00f2n.\n\u00c2tre variet\u00ea.\nA L\u00f6a a turta a se pre\u1e61\u00e9nta scimile, asc\u00ec se cun quarche diffe\u00e9nsa, ad e\u1e61empiu inte l'inpastu inte sta sit\u00ea i ghe m\u00e9ttan asc\u00ec a vaniglia, p\u00e9 arumati\u1e61\u00e2 de ci\u00fc u pi\u00e2ttu, assemme a l'ar\u00e0nciu nu trat\u00f2n. P\u00e9 amurbid\u00ee l'inpastu se ghe p\u00f2 met\u00ee asc\u00ec ina meia renetta."}
