{"id": "28213", "revid": "12552", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28213", "title": "Rocca Barbena", "text": "A Rocca Barbena (1.142 m s.l.m.) a l'\u00e8 ina muntagna de Pre-\u00e0rpe Lig\u00fc(r)i c'a se tr\u00f6va in Pruvinsa de Savuna, inte l'entrut\u00e8ra de Arbenga. A r\u00f2cca a l'\u00e8 cumpletam\u00e8nte in tu terit\u00f4iu cum\u00fcn\u00e2le de Castrevegliu.\nDescrisi\u00f9n.\nA c\u00f2lla a se tr\u00f6va inta cad\u00eana prinsip\u00e2le arp\u00ecna e u suvrasta da settentr\u00ecun a cum\u00fcna de Castrevegliu, a a qu\u00e0le a ghe d\u00e0 u numme in itali\u00e0n (Castelvecchio di Rocca Barbena). U vers\u00e0nte nord u se f\u00e0ccia in sce a gr\u00f2ssa cunca de Barden\u00e8i. Versu nord-ovest a c\u00f2lla du Scravai\u00f9n (814 m) a sep\u00e2(r)a dau Munte Lingu (1103 m), a est u incuntra u sparti\u00e0iva pad\u00e0n lig\u00fc(r)e che u cunt\u00ecnnua cun a c\u00f2lla Gi\u00e0nca (935 m), u munte Subancu (983 m) e u z\u00f9vu de Tui(r)an.\nIn m\u00f2ddu dife(r)\u00e9nte dai \u00e2tri munti da val\u00e2 du N\u00e9va a s\u00ecmma da Rocca a l'\u00e8 frastagli\u00e2 e ruci\u00f9za, prinsipalm\u00e9nte in sce u versante nord. \nAministrativam\u00e9nte u munte u l'\u00e8 parte de Castrevegliu, mentre a livellu de ri\u00e0n u se tr\u00f6va fra e val\u00e0e du Neva e da Burmia de Mil\u00e9ximu.\nIn sce a s\u00ecmma se p\u00f2 vegghe in gr\u00e0n panu(r)\u00e0mma, chi a se \u00ecssa asc\u00ec ina cr\u00f9xe, ai p\u00e9i de sta l\u00ec u se tr\u00f6va u l\u00ecbbru da v\u00e9tta, cun in cuntenit\u00fb de t\u00f2lla p\u00e9 a s\u00f2 prutesi\u00f9n.\nRiv\u00e0ndu aa s\u00ecmma.\nU se p\u00f2 munt\u00e2 in sce a s\u00ecmma da Rocca p\u00e9 a s\u00ea(r)ie de sent\u00e9 chi i p\u00e0rtan da a c\u00f2lla du Scravai\u00f9n, cun ina sc\u00e2(r)a de dificult\u00e0i E, cun di tr\u00e0tti esposti. Se nu u se p\u00f2 segu\u00ee chellu da a c\u00f2lla Gi\u00e0nca.\nT\u00fctti e d\u00f9i i percursi i sun tuc\u00e0i da l'\u00c2ta v\u00eca di munti Lig\u00fc(r)i, c'a p\u00e0ssa de p\u00f2cu a n\u00f2rd daa v\u00e9tta, aa b\u00e0ze da s\u00ecmma, c'a se mustra versu a Val\u00e0 du Burmia.\nPrutesi\u00f9n nat\u00fc(r)\u00e2le.\nA \"Rocca Barbena\" a furma in \u00e0(r)ia prut\u00e8tta pruvins\u00e3le, istitu\u00eca da a Pruvinsa de Savuna, p\u00e9 t\u00fctel\u00e0 e carateristiche ambient\u00e3li e du paes\u00e0ggiu, cun e particulari furme de eruxi\u00f9n carscica.\nA zona a c\u00e2zze dunca dr\u00e9ntu u SIC du Munte Ravin\u00e9t e de Rocca Barbena (cudific\u00e3 cumme \"IT 1324011\")."}
{"id": "28219", "revid": "12552", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28219", "title": "C\u00f2lla du Scravai\u00f9n", "text": "A c\u00f2lla du Scravai\u00f9n (in \u00c8rli \"Scravaijun\", scr\u00eccciu asc\u00ec \"Scravajun\", in it\u00e0lian \"Scravaion\") (814\u00a0m s.l.m.) a l'\u00e8 ina c\u00f2lla e p\u00e0ssu c'u se tr\u00f6va inta cad\u00e9na de \u00c0rpe Lig\u00fc(r)i, in pruvinsa de Sav\u00f9na.\nU cul\u00e9ga u terit\u00f2iu da cum\u00fcna de Castrevegliu, inta val\u00e0 du N\u00e9va, cun Barden\u00e8i, c'u se tr\u00f6va in chella du Burmia.\nDescrisi\u00f9n.\nU p\u00e0ssu u se dr\u00f6ve fra u Munte Lingu (\u00e2tu 1103 m) c'u se tr\u00f6va a pun\u00e8nte de stu chi e a Rocca Barbena. U l'\u00e8 culuc\u00e0u in sce u sparti\u00e0iva da cad\u00e9na prinsip\u00e2le arp\u00ecna, che a div\u00ecdde l'\u00e2ia pad\u00e2na da ch\u00e9lla du bac\u00ecn du M\u00e2 Lig\u00fc(r)e. In sce u versante nord i se tr\u00f6van gr\u00f2sci b\u00f2schi de f\u00f4, anche se u vers\u00e0nte c'u se f\u00e0ccia in sce u M\u00e2 u l'\u00e8 ci\u00fc \u00e0rsu e seccu, v\u00ecsta a ci\u00fc impurtante espusisi\u00f9n au s\u00f9.\nA c\u00f2lla a l'\u00e8 razunzibile andandu da a stradda Nasiun\u00e0le 582 versu Castrevegliu, imbuc\u00e0ndu a Stradda Pruvins\u00e0le 52 che a cul\u00e9ga a lucalit\u00e0i de Ba(r)e\u00e0ssi cun Barden\u00e8i e Ca(r)iss\u00e0n. A s\u00ecmma a l'\u00e8 lunzi 3,5 chilommetri dau sentru du pa\u00ecse, e atret\u00e0nti da Barden\u00e8i.\nIntu puntu de valicu a se tr\u00f6va in \u00e3(r)ia pic-nic e, au de sutta da c\u00f2lla ina veglia ca' cantuni\u00e9ra, in sce u l\u00e0ttu sud, anc\u00f6i abandun\u00e2, ma b\u00e9n vix\u00ecbile daa pruvins\u00e2le. A C\u00f2lla du Scravai\u00f9n u l'\u00e8 puntu de t\u00e0ppa inte l'\u00c2ta V\u00eca di Munti Lig\u00fc(r)i.\nFrequentasi\u00f9n spurt\u00ecva.\nU p\u00e0ssu u l'\u00e8 cunscide(r)\u00e0u cumme ina sal\u00ectta adatta ai ciclisti, sensa mumenti de p\u00e0usa, ma asc\u00ec cun str\u00e0ppi ecescivam\u00e8nte d\u00fci. Munt\u00e0 da S\u00fccca(r)ellu, grassie au sent\u00e9 de Ilaria du Carettu u l'\u00e8 ci\u00fc interes\u00e0nte, grassie asc\u00ec au percursu umbregi\u00e0u inti boschi, cun di bei panu(r)\u00e0mmi. Asc\u00ec u trattu da Stradda Nasiun\u00e2le u l'\u00e8 frequent\u00e0u dai ciclisti, prinsipalmente u l'\u00e8 inse(r)\u00ecu in curse luc\u00e2li, sensa u trafficu de-e macchine. U Scravai\u00f9n u fa parte du clascicu tracci\u00e0u c'u p\u00eca u numme de \"percursu di tr\u00e9i zuvi\", cumprendente asc\u00ec u zuvu de Tui(r)\u00e0n e chellu de Barest\u00ecn."}
{"id": "28221", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28221", "title": "P\u00eao da Cortonn-a", "text": "P\u00eao da Cortonn-a (it: \"Pietro da Cortona\", n\u00f3mme f\u00e2so do \"Pietro Berrettini\") (Cortona, 1\u00b0 nov\u00e9nbre 1596-Romma, 16 mazzo 1669) o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to 'n archit\u00e9tto e 'n pitt\u00f4 itali\u00e0n, in protagon\u00ecsta do bar\u00f2cco.\nV\u00ectta.\nP\u00eao da Cortonn-a o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to 'n ali\u00eavo do Dria Commodi."}
{"id": "28223", "revid": "12552", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28223", "title": "C\u00f2lla de Crava\u00fcna", "text": "A C\u00f2lla de Crava\u00fcna, (o de \"C\u1e5bavaina\" in tu dialettu urmeascu, \"C\u00f2l d Cravaun-a\" in piemunt\u00e9se, \"Colle di Caprauna\" in itali\u00e0n) u l'\u00e8 in p\u00e0ssu de \u00c0rpi Lig\u00fc(r)i, c'u cul\u00e9ga e lucalit\u00e0i de Crava\u00fcna e de Armu, fra e pruvinse de Imp\u00e9(r)ia e de Cuni, ci\u00fc Urmea, pass\u00e0ndu de u P\u00e0ssu de Pre\u00e0llu o \"d' Proa\", da l'urme\u00e0scu (1260 m s.l.m.). U p\u00e0ssu u segna dunca u cunf\u00ecn fra l'ambiente lig\u00fc(r)e (valli Ar\u00f2scia e Pennavaire) e qu\u00e9llu du bac\u00ecn pad\u00e0n (T\u00e0nau).\nDescrisi\u00f9n.\nU p\u00e0ssu u se tr\u00f6va inte \u00c0rpi Marittime, inta divixi\u00f9n de \u00c0rpi Lig\u00fc(r)i, pocu distante da a z\u00f2na prealp\u00ecna. A met\u00e0i fra u Munte da Gu\u00e0rdia e a R\u00f2cca de Penne, u mette in cumunicasi\u00f9n e val\u00e0e du Pennavaire e de l'Ar\u00f2scia, da chi u se zunze poi inta val\u00e0 du T\u00e0nau, anche se u sparti\u00e0iva fra a z\u00f2na idrugrafica Lig\u00fc(r)e e quella Piemuntese u l'\u00e8 indirettu, segn\u00e0u in m\u00f2ddu ci\u00fc n\u00e9ttu dau z\u00e0 d\u00eccciu P\u00e0ssu du Pre\u00e0llu. Inta zona se tr\u00f6van asc\u00ec e s\u00ecmme de Pre-\u00e0rpi Lig\u00fc(r)i, cumme u Munte da Gu\u00e0rdia (1.658 m), a nord est du p\u00e0ssu.\nAmbiente.\nL'ambi\u00e8nte nat\u00fc(r)ale u l'\u00e8 carateris\u00e0u da boschi de f\u00f2, p\u00ecn, niss\u00f6(r)e e l\u00e9rxi, l'\u00e8 dunca r\u00e0i(r)u truv\u00e0 da m\u00e0ccia mediter\u00e0nea, vista l'artit\u00fcdine elev\u00e0. A vegetasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 dunca scimile a quella riscuntrabile in te t\u00fctta sta z\u00f2na arp\u00ecna, se ponan dunca vegghe nu sulu di \u00e8rbui, ma asc\u00ec diferenti tipi de sci\u00f9e inti pr\u00e0i e inti sent\u00e9, cumme di custi de sempit\u00e9rnu o de lav\u00e0nda serv\u00e0iga. Nu mancan poi i anim\u00e0li asc\u00ec, dai s\u00e8rvi ai cravi\u00f6i fin ae l\u00e9vri.\nFrequentasi\u00f9n spurt\u00ecva.\nA zona a l'\u00e8 frequent\u00e0 da tanti apasciun\u00e0i de escursci\u00f9i e arpin\u00ecsmu, se p\u00f2 difatti, da chi, zunze inte muntagne vix\u00ecne, versu l'Armetta (1744m) e u Gal\u00e9 (1708m), fin poi aa C\u00f2lla de San Bertum\u00e9 de Urmea (1446 m), culeg\u00e0u cun u Passu du Pre\u00e0llu (1620m). Chi u se po dunca zunze fin aa vetta de sti munti chi, grassie au percursu de l'\u00c0ta v\u00eca di Munti Lig\u00fc(r)i, de lungu u l'\u00e8 vixitabile u Garb'du Digh\u00e9, in \"arma\", c'u v\u00f6 di \"gr\u00f2tta\" intu dialettu lucale, lungu u sent\u00e9 c'u porta aa c\u00f2lla Bassa (1.851 m), versu Valdinf\u00e9rnu (Garesce).\nFrequent\u00e0u u l'\u00e8 asc\u00ec l'anellu de Crava\u00fcna, che u p\u00e0rte da a burg\u00e0 de Ru\u00f6(r)a e u zunze versu a R\u00f2cca Tramuntina, passandu poi p\u00e9 i sent\u00e9 u se p\u00f2 zunze versu Cantar\u00e0ina o turna inder\u00e9, versu u pa\u00ecse. Chi u se p\u00f2 asc\u00ec pass\u00e0 au rifugiu Ci\u00e0n de l'\u00c0rma (1350m).\nU percusu da Pruvinsale 14-216 u l'\u00e8 asc\u00ec frequent\u00e0u dai ciclisti, chi i partan da Arbenga versu a val\u00e0 du T\u00e0nau, o au cuntr\u00e0iu, partendu da Garesce o da Urmea."}
