{"id": "28346", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28346", "title": "\u0160tasiun da Pi\u00e9na", "text": "A \u0161tasiun da Piena, (\u00ebn lengua fransesa Gare de Pi\u00e8ne, \u00ebn itali\u00e0n \"Stazione di Piena\") la \u00e8 av\u00fca \u00fcna \u0161tasi\u00f9n feruvi\u00e0ria fransesa \u00ebn ra Feruv\u00eca Cuni - V\u00ebnt\u00ebmigl\u2019, che cul\u00ebga p\u00eb 'ra Valada d\u2019 r\u00eb Roja la frasiun da Pi\u00e9na Bassa ( cum\u00fcna d\u00eb Bregl') \u00ebn ra pruvincia d'Nissa.\n\u0160t\u00f2ia.\n\u00dcverta dar 1928, at\u00ecva anant ru 1944 la \u00e8 av\u00fca \u00ebn Italia prima d'ru s\u00ebt\u00e8mbr\u00eb 1947, dopu ru Trat\u00e0 d\u2019 paa\u017e, sci\u00fcr tr\u00f2s entra Vievura e Ra Piena, ra situasiun pulitica la \u00e8 av\u00fca mudific\u00e0a, cun ru tr\u00f2s \u00ebntaram\u00e9nt en Fransa. Bar\u00e0a \u00ebn ru 1944 cun u restu da trata (en-naug\u00fcr\u00e0a e \u00fcverta \u00ebn ru 1970) la \u00e8 l'\u00fcrtima \u0161tasiun fransesa, prima du tr\u00f2s itali\u00e0n."}
{"id": "28347", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28347", "title": "Limicoli", "text": "Con sto n\u00f3mme se int\u00e9nde indic\u00e2 numer\u00f4ze sp\u00eace d'\u00f6xelli d'\u00e6goa \u00f2 m\u00eagio de ripa che apart\u00e9gnan a \u00f3rdini e fam\u00ecgge desp\u00e6ge anche pe dimensci\u00f3n, ma che \u00e0n in cum\u00f9n a m\u00e6xima n\u00ecccia ecol\u00f2gica: pe nutr\u00eese e nidific\u00e2 frequ\u00e9ntan anbienti palud\u00f4zi, z\u00f6ne d'\u00e6goa bassa, f\u00f3ndi de p\u00e2t\u00e0n, s\u00e9gge in \u00e6goa d\u00f4ce che in \u00e6goa s\u00e2, spi\u00e2ge, ma anche proei alag\u00e6, salinn-e, lagunn-e, sm\u00e9uggi. O n\u00f3mme limicoli o vegne da-o lat\u00ecn \"limus\", \"br\u00e0tta\"\".\" O n\u00f3mme o l'\u00e9 anc\u00f3n deuvi\u00f2u inta letiat\u00fba scent\u00ecfica.\nS\u00f3n limicoli i oxelli de famiggie \"Recurvirostridae\", \"Hematopodidae\", \"Burhinidae\",\u00a0\"Charadriidae\", \"Scolopacidae\", tutte drento de l'ordine \"Charadriiformi\"; ma no tutti i Charadriiformi \u00e9n di limicoli - prez\u00e9npio i \"Turnicidae\" (ch'\u00e9n oxelli terestri) o i \"Larida\"e. I \"Glareolidae\" \u00e9n inparent\u00e6 co-i laridae ma \u00e0n abitudine p\u00e6gie a quelle di Limicoli.\nSti \u00f6xelli conv\u00eevan pacificam\u00e9nte into m\u00e6ximo terit\u00f6io, \u00e7\u00e9rcan o \u00e7ibbo a seg\u00f3nda da l\u00f3nghessa de sanpe e a f\u00f3rma do becco, ch'o peu \u00ease l\u00f3ngo, c\u00f9rto, sot\u00ee dr\u00fbo, dr\u00eeto, c\u00f9rvo e a l\u00e6xina. Tanti \u00e8n migrato\u00ee che nid\u00ecfican inte tundre d'Eor\u00f6pa e \u00c0zia e sv\u00e8rnan l\u00f3ngo e c\u00f2ste de l'Atl\u00e0ntico e do Mediterr\u00e0nio Eorop\u00eao e Nord \u00c0frican.\nIn Italia s\u00f3n presenti ci\u00f9 de sciuscianta sp\u00eace, 'na trent\u00e9nn-a se p\u00eauan v\u00e9dde inta salinn-a de Comacchio."}
{"id": "28349", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28349", "title": "Recurvirostridae", "text": "I \"Recurvirostridae\" (Bonaparte, 1854) \u00e9n ina fam\u00ecggia d'\u00f6xelli limicoli, inte l'\u00f3rdine \"Charadriiformes\", co-i generi \"Recurvirostra\", \"Himantopus\" e \"Cladorhynchus.\" D\u00f4e\u00a0sp\u00eace s'atreuvan in Eor\u00f6pa: \"Recurvirostra avosetta\" e \"Himantopus himantopus\"\n\"Moneghinn-a\" (\"Recurvirostra avosetta)\".\nA Moneghinn-a (\"Recurvirostra avosetta\" (Linnaeus, 1758): in itali\u00e0n Avocetta) o l'\u00e9 l'\u00f9nico di Limicoli co-e sanpe parm\u00e6. A l'\u00e9 l\u00f3nga 47 c\u00ectti, co-e g\u00e0nbe l\u00f3nghe\u00a0gr\u00eexo-celestin. Masccio e femina \u00e0n a m\u00e6xima livrea de c\u00f4 gianco e neigro, inconfodibile pe-o sot\u00ee e l\u00f3ngo becco a l\u00e6xina ch'a m\u00e9scia co-o tipico movimento laterale d'\u00f2scila\u00e7i\u00f3n da sin\u00ecstra a d\u00e9stra e vicev\u00e8rsa a f\u00ee d'\u00e6goa pe nutr\u00ecse. \n\u00d3xello migrat\u00f4 o l'ar\u00ecva in Primav\u00e8ia, o predil\u00ecgge z\u00f6ne \u00f9mide, \u00c0to Adri\u00e0tico, Pal\u00f9ddi Toscann-e, Valli da pesca, G\u00f3rfo de C\u00e0liari, laghi Poli\u00e9ixi, Sic\u00eclia.\nO\u00a0nid\u00ecfica a N\u00f2rd\u00a0in c\u00f2ste fang\u00f4ze; a f\u00e2 o n\u00eeo in t\u00e6ra, 3-4 \u00eauve c\u00f4v\u00e6 da t\u00f9tti do\u00ee\u00a0pe 22-23 gi\u00f3rni. I pol\u00ecn nid\u00eef\u00fbghi x\u00eauan d\u00f2ppo in m\u00e9ize.\n\"G\u00e0nbe l\u00f3nghe\" \u00f2 \"Sigh\u00e9ugna\" (\"Himantopus himantopus\").\n\"G\u00e0nbe l\u00f3nghe\" \u00f2 \"Sigh\u00e9ugna\" \"(Himantopus himantopus\" (Linnaeus, 1758); in itali\u00e0n \"Cavaliere d'Italia\") o l'\u00e9 'n \u00f6xello men\u00fbo l\u00f3ngo 40 c\u00ectti, de c\u00f4 gi\u00e0nco co-o d\u00f2rso, e \u00e2e e o becco n\u00e9igri; e ganbe l\u00f3nghiscime de c\u00f4 r\u00eauza; o peu av\u00e9i o cop\u00f9sso n\u00e9igro (livrea nu\u00e7i\u00e2le), a femina a l'\u00e9 mar\u00f2n. O becco o l'\u00e9 dr\u00eeto sot\u00ee.\nIn Italia o nid\u00ecfica in Delta Po, Orbetello, Sard\u00e9gna, Parco do Mincio, F\u00f4xe Iz\u00f3nso, in Meridi\u00f3n inti laghi de Lesina e Varano, Salinn-a Marg\u00e0ita de Savoia, Sicilia."}
