{"id": "28405", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28405", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Genola", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Genola, (in italian \"Stazione di Genola\") a l'\u00e8 st\u00e6ta inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a c'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 linia Turin-Sann-a, averta a part\u00ec dao 1855, a l'\u00e8 st\u00e6ta ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Genola, in Provinsa de Cuneo, fin a l'\u00e0nno 2003, d\u00e6ta da s\u00f2 sopresci\u00f3n, in moddo sc\u00eemile a quanto avegnuo con a Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Cosceria (in Provinsa de Sann-a) e asc\u00ec quella de Santena Tetti Giro.\nInpianti.\nLont\u00e0na dao \u00e7\u00e9ntro de Genola qu\u00e0xi 2 chilometri, a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a prez\u00e9nta dui ci\u00e6n distinti, chi i l'\u00e9an douvi\u00e6 fin aa s\u00f2 sopresci\u00f2n. Acheu a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a v\u00e8rsa inte 'na sitoa\u00e7i\u00f3n de aband\u00f3n, \u00e7er\u00e2 ao p\u00f9blico con i ac\u00e8ssi mu\u00e2i."}
