{"id": "28758", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28758", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de T\u00e0ggia-\u00c0rma", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de T\u00e0ggia-\u00c0rma (in italian \"Stazione di Taggia-Arma\") a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a c'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 Ferov\u00eea Z\u00eana-Vintim\u00ecggia, averta a part\u00ec dao 2001, a l'e ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Taggia e da s\u00f2 fra\u00e7i\u00f3n Arma inta Provinsa de Inp\u00e9ria\nSt\u00f2ia.\nA l'\u00e8 st\u00e6ta averta into 2001, p\u00e9 sostito\u00ee quella v\u00e9ggia in contemporanea con l'ativa\u00e7i\u00f3n do neuvo tr\u00e0tto fra San Loenso e Bordighea. \nInpianti.\n\u2022 Segondo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de\u00a0 a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7ion de categor\u00eea \"d'arg\u00e9nto\"."}
{"id": "28759", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28759", "title": "Stasi\u00f9n de Inpeia", "text": "A stasi\u00f9n de Inpeia, (in zen\u00e9\u015be \"Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Inp\u00e9ria\", in arbengan\u00e9\u015be \"Stasi\u00f9n de Imp\u00e9ia\", in italian \"Stazione di Imperia\") a l'\u00e8 ina stasiun feruvi\u00e0ria italiana ch'a se tr\u00f6va in sci\u00e0 Zena-Vintim\u00efa, v\u00e8rb\u00fca a part\u00ec dau 2016, a l'e au servissiu da cum\u00fcna de Inp\u00e9ja s\u00e9de da Pruvinsa cun u nomme pa\u00e9scu.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nI primmi tav\u00e0ji p\u00e9 l'ativasi\u00f9n da tr\u00e0tta i sun st\u00e2i tu f\u00e2iti ai inissi du 2016, cun a custrusi\u00f9n di pr\u00ecmmi l\u00f2tti da feruv\u00eca, ma a p\u00e9 u n\u00f6vu inpi\u00e0ntu u l'\u00e8 st\u00e2itu ativ\u00e2u in ci\u00e0n spart\u00ecu in tr\u00e9i mumenti, u primmu fra u 4 e u 25 de \u015b\u00fcgnu, u segundu d\u00fcante a st\u00e8 e a f\u00e0\u015be ci\u00fc inpurtante a cumens\u00e0 dau nuv\u00e9nbre de c\u00f6ll'\u00e0nnu, che u l'\u00e0 purt\u00e2u a l'inseim\u00e9ntu di \u00fcrtimi dettaji, cumme e sc\u00e2e m\u00f2bili e daa magiur\u00e2nsa di servissi esensi\u00e2li, cuntempuraneamente u l'\u00e8 st\u00e2itu ci\u00f2su u tr\u00e0ttu fra San Luensu e Arassce, p\u00e9 cunsent\u00ec u rac\u00f2rdu fra u n\u00f6vu e u v\u00e9ju traci\u00e2u.\nA stasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 st\u00e2ita dunca v\u00e8rb\u00fca u 19 de dex\u00e8nbre du 2016, insemme au n\u00f6vu toccu de f\u00e8ruvia ch'u l'a f\u00e2itu divent\u00e0 ci\u00f2se e stasi\u00f9i de Di\u00e0n, Ineia, U P\u00f2rtu, S\u00earvu-San Bertum\u00ea e And\u00f6a.\nA part\u00ec dau \u015ben\u00e0 du 2017, sun st\u00e2ite ativ\u00e2e e prused\u00fce p\u00e9 permette l'i\u015bulamentu di anbi\u00e8nti dai soi, p\u00e9 l'ar\u00ecvu da pustasi\u00f9n da pulis\u00eca feruvi\u00e0ria e asc\u00ec in previxi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 st\u00e2ita l'avert\u00fca de in st\u00e2ncu, dunde se p\u00f2nan acat\u00e0 giurnali e \u00e0utre c\u00f4se.\nParte de c\u00f6lli travaji i sun st\u00e2iti termin\u00e2i entru u periudu de scadensa previstu, indic\u00e2u cumme \u015b\u00fcgnu du 2017, nunustante che i nun s\u00f9n manc\u00e2e e critiche da chi d\u00f6v\u00f6a de lungu a stasiun, che rispettu a qu\u00e9lle veje, ci\u00fc vix\u00ecne ai quart\u00ea d'Ineia e du P\u00f2rtu, a\u00f9 rip\u00ef\u00e0bili sulu cun a machina o cun a curiera.\nPropiu p\u00e9 stu f\u00e2itu chi a cum\u00fcna a l'\u00e0 dec\u00ec\u015bu de mette m\u00e0n aa \u015bona da stasi\u00f9n, vistu che au 2020 u st\u00e2ncu u l'\u00e9a anc\u00f9 ci\u00f2su e che i manc\u00e0van asc\u00ec de segnalasi\u00f9i adegu\u00e2e. Intu pa\u00e9scu periudu u l'\u00e8 st\u00e2itu pre\u015bent\u00e2u u prugettu p\u00e9 culeg\u00e0 a stasiun cun a p\u00ecsta ciclabile intu veju traci\u00e2u da feruv\u00eca, grassie a l'alargamentu da str\u00e0dda vixin aa s-ci\u00fcm\u00e2ia.\nInpianti.\nA stasi\u00f9n gh'a quattru bin\u00e2i p\u00e9 u trasp\u00f2rtu di passeg\u00e9i e dui fabric\u00e2i viagiat\u00f9i, segundu a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a stasiun de\u00a0Inpeia a l'\u00e8 ina stasiun de categu\u00efa \"d'\u00f4u\".\nServissi.\n\u2022 Spurtellu de b\u00efette\u00eca\n\u2022 B\u00efette\u00eca autumati\u015b\u00e0\n\u2022 Sal\u00f9n d'at\u00e9\u015ba\n\u2022 Servissi igenici \n\u2022 P\u00f2stu da Pulis\u00eca feruviaria\nInterscangi.\nA stasi\u00f9n a se tr\u00f6va distante dai servissi da sit\u00e0i, p\u00e9 questu u l'\u00e8 st\u00e2u rimudern\u00e2u u calend\u00e2iu de curse de curi\u00eare, che e cunsent\u00e0n ina m\u00e9ju cuvert\u00fca du tr\u00e0fegu.\n\u2022 Curi\u00eare RT du trasportu p\u00fcbrivu luc\u00e0le da Pruvinsa de Inp\u00e9ia.\n\u2022 Tasc\u00ec."}
{"id": "28787", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28787", "title": "Zapopan", "text": "Zapopan (pronon\u00e7i\u00e2 , in nahuatl \"Tzapopan\") a l'\u00e8 'na \u00e7it\u00e6 mescic\u00e0nn-a ch'a s'atr\u00eauva dr\u00e9nto a l'\u00e0rea \u00fbrbana da \u00e7it\u00e6 de Guadalajara, a seg\u00f3nda ci\u00f9 inport\u00e0nte do P\u00e0ize e capol\u00eaugo do st\u00e2to feder\u00e6 de Jalisco. Co-ina popola\u00e7i\u00f3n de 1.476.491 (a-o censim\u00e9nto do 2020) o l'\u00e8 o ci\u00f9 gr\u00e0nde monic\u00ecpio do s\u00f2 st\u00e2to, ci\u00f9 do capol\u00eaugo m\u00e6ximo, e o s\u00e8timo in t\u00f9tto o M\u00e9scico."}
