{"id": "28790", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28790", "title": "Stasi\u00f9n de Di\u00e0n", "text": "A stasi\u00f9n de Di\u00e0n, (in italian \"Stazione di Diano\", in zene\u015be \"Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Di\u00e0n\"), a l'\u00e8 ina stasi\u00f9n feruvi\u00e0ria itali\u00e2na ch'a se tr\u00f6va in scia Zena-Vintim\u00efa, v\u00e8rb\u00fca a part\u00ec dau 2016, a l'e au servissiu de cum\u00fcne de Dian San P\u00ea, U Castellu de Di\u00e0n e du vix\u00ecn terit\u00f4iu da Ma\u00ecna de Di\u00e0n, t\u00fctti tr\u00e9i inta Pruvinsa de Inp\u00e9ia.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nA stasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 st\u00e0 v\u00e8rb\u00fca u 19 de dex\u00e8nbre du 2016, insemme au n\u00f6vu toccu de f\u00e8ruvia ch'u l'a f\u00e2u divent\u00e0 ci\u00f2se e stasi\u00f9i de Di\u00e0n, Ineia, U P\u00f2rtu, S\u00earvu-San Bertum\u00ea e And\u00f6a. Sta chi a se tr\u00f6va me\u015b\u015ba inta cum\u00fcna de Dian San P\u00ea e me\u015b\u015ba inte quella du Cast\u00e9llu.\nInpianti.\n\u2022 Segundu a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a stasi\u00f9n de\u00a0Dian a l'\u00e8 ina stasi\u00f9n de categu\u00efa \"d'arg\u00e9nto\".\nInterscangi.\nA stasi\u00f9n a se tr\u00f6va distante dai servissi da sit\u00e0i, p\u00e9 questu u l'\u00e8 st\u00e2u rimudern\u00e2u u calend\u00e2iu de curse de curi\u00eare, che e cunsent\u00e0n ina m\u00e9ju cuvert\u00fca du tr\u00e0fegu.\nServissi.\n\u2022 Curi\u00eare RT du trasportu p\u00fcbrivu luc\u00e0le da Pruvinsa de Inp\u00e9ia.\n\u2022 Tasc\u00ec."}
{"id": "28791", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28791", "title": "Stasi\u00f9n de Fin\u00f4 Marina", "text": "A stasi\u00f9n de Fin\u00f4 Marina (in sen\u00e9ise \"Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n da Fin\u00e2 M\u00e6nn-a\", in talian \"Stazione di Finale Ligure Marina\") a l'\u00e8 \u00fcna stasi\u00f9n f\u00e9ruvi\u00e0ria in-scia l\u00ecnia S\u00e9na-Vintim\u00eea, scitu\u00f4 tra du\u00e8i garbassi in-tu t\u00f6ccu l\u00fccale che u va da Savuna a Inperia. A l'\u00e8, da-a ser\u00f4 de stasiu\u00e8i de Pia e de Varigotti in-tu 1977, a sula ferm\u00f4 a-a giurn\u00f4 d'anc\u00f6 a-u servissiu du cum\u00fcne de Fin\u00f4 e de cu\u00e9lli vex\u00ecn. \nA stasi\u00f9n a se truva in-scia ciassa \"Vittorio Veneto\", ar\u00e9nte a-a SS1 Aurelia, ci\u00fc o menu a 200 metri da-u m\u00f4 e a 500 da-u c\u00e9ntru du paise. \nSt\u00f2ia.\nAv\u00e9rta in-tu 1872, insemme a-u restu da f\u00e9ruv\u00eea tra Savuna e Vintim\u00eea, a l'\u00e9ra inprinsipiu ciam\u00f4 \"Stazione di Finalmarina\", pe poi cangi\u00f4 u s\u00f6 numme in \"Stazione di Finale Ligure (Marina)\" da-a creasi\u00f9n du cum\u00fcne de Fin\u00f4 in-tu 1927.\nU frabic\u00f9n vi\u00e9ggitu\u00e8i duver\u00f9n ancura d'anc\u00f6 u l'\u00e8 st\u00e9tu custruiu in-tu 1938, segundu u prug\u00e8ttu de l'archit\u00e9ttu Roberto Narducci.\nStrut\u00fce e inpianti.\nA stasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 furm\u00f4 da \u00fcn frabic\u00f9n vi\u00e9ggitu\u00e8i, da tr\u00e9i banchin che i servan e cuattru culisse pasanti e de \u00fcn sc\u00f4ru pe-e merse.\nE culisse a dispusisi\u00f9n pe-a ferm\u00f4 e u pasaggiu di tr\u00e9ni i s\u00f9n cuattru e, in-ta ci\u00fc parte di c\u00f4xi (dunca in cundisiu\u00e8i de sirculasi\u00f9n regul\u00f4 e sensa retardi), i tr\u00e9ni che i rivan in-ta stasi\u00f9n i s\u00f9n cusc\u00ec spart\u00ee:\nMuvim\u00e9ntu.\nIn-ta stasi\u00f9n de Fin\u00f4 Marina i ferman scu\u00e9xi t\u00fctti i tr\u00e9ni che i pasan de chi.\nServissi.\nA stasi\u00f9n de Fin\u00f4 Marina, che a l'\u00e8 cunscider\u00f4 da RFI cumme de categuria \"arg\u00e9ntu\", a l'\u00e0:\nInterscangi.\nIn-ta ciassa \"Vittorio Veneto\", ar\u00e9nte a-a stasi\u00f9n, a gh'\u00e8 \u00fcna ferm\u00f4 (e capul\u00ecnia) de curiere gestie da-a TPL. Chi se ferman asci e curiere da ditta \"SAR Autolinee della Riviera\"."}
{"id": "28792", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28792", "title": "Sta\u00e7ion de And\u00eaua", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de And\u00eaua, (in arbengan\u00e9ize e inperi\u00e9ize \"Stasi\u00f9n de And\u00f6a\", in italian \"Stazione di Andora\") a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria italiann-a c'a se treuva in sci\u00e2 Ferov\u00eea Z\u00eana-Vintim\u00ecggia, averta a part\u00ec dao 2016, a l'e ao servi\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Andeua inta Provinsa de Sann-a.\nInpianti.\n\u2022 Segondo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de\u00a0 a l'\u00e8 inn-a sta\u00e7ion de categor\u00eea \"bronzo\"."}
