{"id": "28819", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28819", "title": "Stasi\u00f9n de Arbenga", "text": "A Stasi\u00f9n de Arbenga, (in zenese \"Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Arbenga\", in italian \"Stazione di Albenga\"), a l'\u00e8 ina stasi\u00f9n feruvi\u00e0ria italiana c'a se tr\u00f6va in scia feruv\u00eca Zena-Vintim\u00eea, averta a part\u00ec dau 1872, a l'e au servissiu du cum\u00fcn de Arbenga inta pruvinsa de Savuna.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nA stasi\u00f9n a l'\u00e8 sta averta intu 1872 assemme a t\u00fcttu u t\u00f2ccu fra Sav\u00f9na e Vintim\u00eca u 25 de z\u00fcgnu de quel'\u00e0nnu. Inisialmente u fabric\u00e0u viagiat\u00f9i u l'\u00e9a in l\u00e9gnu, cumme quellu de A(r)\u00e0sce, poi sustitu\u00eca cun a strut\u00fca d'anc\u00f6i d\u00fcante a custrusi\u00f9n du bin\u00e2iu d\u00f9ggiu fra e stasi\u00f9i de Arbenga e L\u00f6a.\nI trav\u00e0i p\u00e9 u segundu bin\u00e0iu e da n\u00f6va stasi\u00f9n i sun vegn\u00fci a part\u00ec dau 1936, p\u00e9 av\u00e9 in impiantu p\u00e9 recamp\u00e0 m\u00e9iu e m\u00e8rci e asc\u00ec p\u00e9 da in acui\u00e8nsa ci\u00fc favurevule ai viaggiat\u00f9i. L'architettu c'u l'ha pruget\u00e0u a stasi\u00f9n u l'\u00e9a Roberto Narducci, u pa\u00e9ggiu da stasi\u00f9n de L\u00f6a.\nL'edifissiu u vegne cusc\u00ec r\u00e9zu \u00fctiliz\u00e0bile a part\u00ec dau 1937, asc\u00ec se u l'ha sub\u00ecu di rimudernamenti a part\u00ec dai \u00e0nni 2000, che nu u l'h\u00e0n strav\u00f2ltu cumunque i esterni. \nImpianti.\n\u2022 Segundu a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a stasi\u00f9n de Arbenga a l'\u00e8 ina stasiun de categu\u00eca \"d'arz\u00e9ntu\".\nInterscangi.\n\u2022 Curi\u00eare TPL linea\u00a0du trasportu p\u00fcbbricu luc\u00e0le da pruvinsa de Savuna.\n\u2022 Tasc\u00ec."}
