{"id": "28876", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28876", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana V\u00eaxima", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana V\u00eaxima (asc\u00ec s\u00f4lo sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de V\u00eaxima, in itali\u00e0n \"Stazione di Genova Vesima\") a l'\u00e9 'na sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria itali\u00e0nn-a ch'a se tr\u00eauva in sci\u00e2 ferov\u00eea Z\u00eana-Vintim\u00ecggia. Av\u00e8rta a part\u00ee da-o 1868, a l'\u00e9 a-o serv\u00ec\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Z\u00eana, capol\u00eaugo da s\u00f2 \u00e7it\u00e6 metropolit\u00e0nn-a, pi-\u00e2 fra\u00e7i\u00f3n de V\u00eaxima, p\u00e0rte de l'unit\u00e6 urban\u00ecstica de Cr\u00eavai do Monic\u00ecpio VII Pon\u00e9nte (circoscri\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri).\nSt\u00f6ia.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana V\u00eaxima a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta inougur\u00e2 inte l'\u00e0nno 1868, a-o mom\u00e9nto de l'avert\u00fba do t\u00f2cco de ferov\u00eea conpr\u00e9izo tra e d\u00f4e sta\u00e7io\u00ecn de \u00d4tri e de S\u00e0nn-a.\nInpi\u00e0nti.\nInta sta\u00e7i\u00f3n gh'\u00e9 s\u00f4lo d\u00f4e col\u00ecsse pas\u00e0nti e 'na gr\u00e0nde banch\u00ecnn-a m\u00ecssa a-o s\u00f2 c\u00e9ntro, coleg\u00e2 a-a Str\u00e0dda Our\u00e9lia pe m\u00eazo de 'n sotopas\u00e0ggio. A banch\u00ecnn-a a l'\u00e9 decor\u00e2 da v\u00e0rri giardin\u00e9tti con \u00e8rboi, p\u00e0rme e \u00e2tri t\u00eepi de ci\u00e0nte. No gh'\u00e9 de bigeter\u00eea e o fabric\u00e2to vi\u00e2giato\u00ee, scito\u00f2u in sci\u00e2 banch\u00ecnn-a tra e d\u00f4e col\u00ecsse, d\u00f2ppo \u00ease st\u00e6to convert\u00eeo in abita\u00e7i\u00f3n priv\u00e2, in sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to do t\u00f9tto ser\u00f2u.\nSeg\u00f3ndo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de\u00a0V\u00eaxima a l'\u00e8 'na ferm\u00e2ta de categor\u00eea \"br\u00f3nzo\".\nMovim\u00e9nto.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana V\u00eaxima a l'\u00e9 serv\u00eea s\u00f4lo da colegam\u00e9nti region\u00e2li e metropolit\u00e9n de \"Trenitalia\", inte l'\u00e0nbito do s\u00f2 contr\u00e0tto de serv\u00ec\u00e7io co-a Regi\u00f3n Lig\u00f9ria, co-in tr\u00e0fego ch'o l'\u00e9 per\u00f2 limit\u00f2u a-o s\u00f4lo per\u00eeodo est\u00eevo. Apr\u00eauvo a-o s\u00f2 sc\u00e0rso tr\u00e0fego ferovi\u00e0rio, a l'\u00e9 l'\u00f9nica tra e 23 sta\u00e7io\u00ecn zen\u00e9ixi gest\u00eee da RFI d\u00f3nde no gh'\u00e9 'na ferm\u00e2ta regol\u00e2re di tr\u00eani do serv\u00ec\u00e7io ferovi\u00e0rio urb\u00e2no da \u00e7it\u00e6.\nServ\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana V\u00eaxima a no disp\u00f3nn-e de nisci\u00f9n serv\u00ec\u00e7io in particol\u00e2. L\u00f3ngo o l\u00e2to da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n v\u00e8rso o m\u00e2 gh'\u00e9 'n parch\u00e9zzo pe-e outom\u00f2bili.\nIntersc\u00e0ngi.\nDa-ar\u00e9nte a-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n, in sce l'Our\u00e9lia, gh'\u00e9 a ferm\u00e2ta de cori\u00eare de \"V\u00eaxima\" (\"Vesima\")."}
{"id": "28877", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28877", "title": "Sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana \u00d4tri", "text": "A sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana \u00d4tri (asc\u00ec s\u00f4lo sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri, in itali\u00e0n \"Stazione di Genova Voltri\") a l'\u00e9 'na sta\u00e7i\u00f3n ferovi\u00e0ria itali\u00e0nn-a ch'a se tr\u00eauva in sci\u00e2 ferov\u00eea Z\u00eana-Vintim\u00ecggia. Av\u00e8rta a part\u00ee da-o 1868, a l'\u00e9 a-o serv\u00ec\u00e7io do com\u00f9n de Z\u00eana, capol\u00eaugo da s\u00f2 \u00e7it\u00e6 metropolit\u00e0nn-a, pi-\u00e2 delega\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri.\nSt\u00f6ia.\nA pr\u00ecmma sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana \u00d4tri a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta inougur\u00e2 inte l'\u00e0nno 1868, a-o mom\u00e9nto de l'avert\u00fba do t\u00f2cco de ferov\u00eea conpr\u00e9izo tra sta localit\u00e6 chi e a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de S\u00e0nn-a.\nInte l'\u00f2cax\u00f3n do rad\u00f3pio da l\u00ecnia ferovi\u00e0ria tra \u00d4tri e V\u00e2ze, conplet\u00f2u into 1970, l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to av\u00e8rto o n\u00eauvo fabric\u00e2to vi\u00e2giato\u00ee, costro\u00eeo in sci\u00e2 n\u00eauva l\u00ecnia, scito\u00e2 ci\u00f9 v\u00e8rso m\u00f3nte, e dot\u00f2u da qu\u00e9llo \u00e0nno do sc\u00e0gno do diret\u00f4 movim\u00e9nto, da s\u00e2la d'at\u00e9iza e do caf\u00e8. A \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo o v\u00eagio cazam\u00e9nto o l'\u00e9 anc\u00f3n in \u00fbzo, d\u00e6to ch'o se tr\u00eauva in sc\u00ea col\u00ecsse de t\u00e9sta d\u00eauvi\u00e6 pe-i tr\u00eani urb\u00e2ni che n\u00e0scian chi.\nInpi\u00e0nti.\nPasag\u00ea.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri, scib\u00e9n ch'a se tr\u00eauva inta perifer\u00eea a l'estr\u00eamo pon\u00e9nte da \u00e7it\u00e6 de Z\u00eana, a l'\u00e0 'na \u00e7\u00e8rta inport\u00e0nsa p\u00f2-u trasp\u00f2rto p\u00f9blico loc\u00e2le. Def\u00e6ti, a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 un di do\u00ee capol\u00ecnia di tr\u00eani metropolit\u00e9n ch'atrav\u00e8rsan a \u00e7it\u00e6, con l'\u00e2tra estremit\u00e6 ch'a se tr\u00eauva in corispond\u00e9nsa da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana N\u00e8rvi.\nScito\u00e2 inta p\u00e0rte de lev\u00e0nte do quart\u00ea, a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a disp\u00f3nn-e de d\u00f4e col\u00ecsse pas\u00e0nti in sci\u00e2 l\u00ecnia prin\u00e7ip\u00e2le, sc\u00ecnn-a l'ag\u00f3sto do 2019 colegh\u00e6 da 'n sorvap\u00e0sso. Sto pas\u00e0ggio chi o l'\u00e9 per\u00f2 st\u00e6to ser\u00f2u apr\u00eauvo a di probl\u00eami strutut\u00e2li e caci\u00f2u zu into 2020; d\u00f3nca, pe an\u00e2 da 'na p\u00e0rte a l'\u00e2tra da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n, se dov\u00e9iva pas\u00e2 da-o p\u00f3nte da Str\u00e0dda Our\u00e9lia in sci\u00e2 ferov\u00eea. In sci\u00e2 f\u00ecn, co-\u00een investim\u00e9nto de 1,4 milio\u00ecn de \u00e9ori, l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to instal\u00f2u 'n n\u00eauvo sorvap\u00e0sso, av\u00f2u inta n\u00e9utte tra o 24 e o 25 de set\u00e9nbre do 2022 e av\u00e8rto a-i ut\u00e9nti da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a-i 10 d'\u00f2t\u00f4bre.\nGh'\u00e9 d\u00f4e col\u00ecsse de t\u00e9sta asc\u00ec, scito\u00e6 v\u00e8rso o m\u00e2 in corispond\u00e9nsa da v\u00eagia sta\u00e7i\u00f3n, ser\u00e2 qu\u00e0nde a l\u00ecnia, pe po\u00e9i \u00ease radogi\u00e2, a l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta aretr\u00e2 da l\u00f3ngo a c\u00f2sta a 'na \u00e7entan\u00e2 de m\u00eatri inder\u00ea. St'inpi\u00e0nto chi, sp\u00e9cce a col\u00ecssa ci\u00f9 a n\u00f2rd d\u00e6to che qu\u00e9lla de t\u00e9sta n\u00f9mero 2 a no l'\u00e9 atoalm\u00e9nte in \u00fbzo, o l'\u00e9 d\u00eauvi\u00f2u p\u00f2-u ri\u00e7evim\u00e9nto e a part\u00e9nsa di tr\u00eani metropolit\u00e9n. Pe de ci\u00f9, v\u00e8rso lev\u00e0nte, gh'\u00e9 'na col\u00ecssa de preced\u00e9nsa s\u00e9nsa marciap\u00ea ch'a l'\u00e9 l\u00f3nga 460 m\u00eatri.\nSeg\u00f3ndo a clasc\u00ecfica de RFI a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri a l'\u00e9 'na sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de categor\u00eea \"d'arg\u00e9nto\".\nM\u00e8r\u00e7e.\nA lev\u00e0nte da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n gh'\u00e9 'n colegam\u00e9nto co-o lanbr\u00e9 pe-i cont\u00e9ine scito\u00f2u into p\u00f2rto PSA de Pra, ciam\u00f2u Z\u00eana Pra M\u00e2. Da-o labr\u00e9 gh'\u00e9 def\u00e6ti 'n colegam\u00e9nto dir\u00e9tto s\u00e9gge con \u00d4tri, e d\u00f3nca co-a l\u00ecnia pe S\u00e0nn-a, che v\u00e8rso lev\u00e0nte co-a l\u00ecnia prin\u00e7ip\u00e2le pe Z\u00eana S\u00e0n P\u00ea d'\u00c6nn-a. Gh'\u00e9 asc\u00ec 'n colegam\u00e9nto co-a l\u00ecnia \u00c0sti-Z\u00eana (e d\u00f3nca con Lisci\u00e0ndria pe m\u00eazo da Lisci\u00e0ndria-\u00c0cqui) gr\u00e0\u00e7ie a-o n\u00eauvo t\u00f2cco in galer\u00eea da cosc\u00ec d\u00eeta bert\u00e8lla de Pra, ch'o s'un\u00ecsce a-e l\u00ecnie che v\u00e0n v\u00e8rso n\u00f2rd in corispond\u00e9nsa da sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana B\u00f2rzoi.\nO p\u00e0rco m\u00e8r\u00e7e de Z\u00eana Pra M\u00e2 o l'\u00eaa form\u00f2u de qu\u00e0ttro col\u00ecsse ma, inte l'\u00e0nbito di trav\u00e0ggi p\u00f2-u poten\u00e7iam\u00e9nto do gr\u00f3ppo ferovi\u00e0rio de Z\u00eana e da realiza\u00e7i\u00f3n do t\u00e8rso v\u00e0lico, e col\u00ecsse s\u00f3n divent\u00e6 s\u00eai e gh'\u00e9 za o prog\u00e8tto pe ariv\u00e2 a \u00e9utto. O rac\u00f2rdio ferovi\u00e0rio co-o p\u00f2rto, che pe t\u00e0nto t\u00e9npo o l'\u00eaa rest\u00f2u a 'na s\u00f4la col\u00ecssa, o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to radogi\u00f2u a-o prin\u00e7\u00ecpio do 2020.\nMovim\u00e9nto.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de Z\u00eana \u00d4tri a l'\u00e9 serv\u00eea da-i colegam\u00e9nti region\u00e2li de \"Trenitalia\" inte l'\u00e0nbito do s\u00f2 contr\u00e0tto de serv\u00ec\u00e7io co-a Regi\u00f3n Lig\u00f9ria, sorviat\u00f9tto ligh\u00e6 a-o serv\u00ec\u00e7io ferovi\u00e0rio urb\u00e2no de Z\u00eana.\nIn particol\u00e2, e col\u00ecsse pas\u00e0nti s\u00f3n atrav\u00e8rs\u00e6 da-i tr\u00eani region\u00e2li che v\u00e0n in dire\u00e7i\u00f3n S\u00e0nn-a, Vintim\u00ecggia, S\u00e9stri Lev\u00e0nte e Sp\u00e9zza Centr\u00e2le m\u00e9ntre, inte col\u00ecsse che fin\u00ecscian inte sta sta\u00e7i\u00f3n chi, se f\u00e8rman i conv\u00f2lli do serv\u00ec\u00e7io urb\u00e2no, ch'o se svil\u00f9ppa pr\u00f2pio tra a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n de \u00d4tri e qu\u00e9lla de N\u00e8rvi.\nServ\u00ec\u00e7\u00e7i.\nA sta\u00e7i\u00f3n a disp\u00f3nn-e de:\nIntersc\u00e0ngi.\nDa-ar\u00e9nte a-a sta\u00e7i\u00f3n gh'\u00e9 e ferm\u00e2te de cori\u00eare de \"Vintim\u00ecggia (1 e 2)/B\u00f3ffa\" (\"Ventimiglia/Buffa\"), \"B\u00f3ffa 1/Vintim\u00ecggia\" (\"Buffa 1/Ventimiglia\"), \"B\u00f3ffa 2/Veit\u00e6\" (\"Buffa 2/Verit\u00e0\"), \"\u00d4tri/\u00d4tri FS\" (\"Voltri/Voltri FS\"), \"\u00d4tri FS/Capol\u00ecnia\" (\"Voltri FS/Capolinea\"), \"Veit\u00e6/\u00d4tri FS\" (Verit\u00e0/Voltri FS) e \"Parks/Veit\u00e6\" (\"Parks/Verit\u00e0\")."}
{"id": "28878", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28878", "title": "ATP Esercizio", "text": "ATP Esercizio l'\u00e9 unna so\u00e7iet\u00e6 \u00e0 responsabilit\u00e6 limit\u00e2 soggetta a-a dire\u00e7ion e o coordinamento de AMT Genova ch'a t\u00ebgne a ci\u00f9 parte do seu capit\u00e2 so\u00e7i\u00e2. A l'\u00e9 st\u00e6ta accord\u00e4ia do transp\u00f2rto pubrico inti 67 comuni da \u00e7itt\u00e6 metropolita\u00f1a de Zena e inte atri communi de provin\u00e7e vixi\u00f1e de Sa\u00f1a (Vaze, L'Orba), da Speza (Maissa\u00f1a, Vaise, O Caro, Deiva, Framua, Bonasseua, Levanto), di Pia\u00e7ensa (\u00d6ton), Parma (Bed\u00f2nia) e Lisciandria (Arqu\u00e2) fin a-i 31 de dexembre do 2020.\nIst\u00f6ia.\nA nascion da dita d'ancheu a v\u00ebgne da-i 21 de dexembre do 2005 da-a fuxon pe incorpora\u00e7ion de \"ALI Autolinee Liguri Provincia di Genova S.p.A\". inta \"Tigullio Pubblici Trasporti S.p.A.\", e doe dite che e garantivan o servi\u00e7io de transp\u00f2rto pubrico into territ\u00f6io metropolitan, ma a-o de feua do territ\u00f6io da capit\u00e2 (gestio da AMT); a neuva dita a l'\u00e0 piggiou o nomme de ATP - Azienda Trasporti Provinciali S.p.A..\nA\u00e7ienda.\nCapit\u00e2 da dita.\nO capit\u00e2 da dita l'\u00e9 scompartio cosc\u00ec:"}
{"id": "28885", "revid": "1211", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28885", "title": "Burhinidae", "text": "Burhinidae (Mathews, 1912) a l'\u00e9 'na famiggia d'\u00f6xelli limicoli inte l'\u00f3rdine \"Charadriiformes\". \u00c9n prez\u00e9nti inte regio\u00ecn tropic\u00e2li de t\u00f9tto o m\u00f3ndo ma anche in Eor\u00f6pa e in Oustr\u00e0lia. \u00c0n f\u00f2rti becchi, \u00e9uggi gi\u00e0ni, ganbe l\u00f3nghe de c\u00f4 mim\u00e9tico. \n\"Burhinus oedicnemus\" a l'\u00e9 a s\u00f4la menn-a prez\u00e9nte in Italia e co-in n\u00f3mme zeneize registr\u00f2u da-o Paganini: Scuriat\u00f3n. \nScistem\u00e0tica e nommi.\nInta clasifica\u00e7i\u00f3n de Linneo i \"Burhinidae\" \u00eaan scito\u00e6 inte l'\u00f3rdine Grallae, e o Scoriat\u00f3n o l'aiva o nomme \"Charadrius oedicnemus.\"\nA-o di d'ancheu o no f\u00e2 ci\u00f9 parte do genere \"Charadrius\", scib\u00e9n che seg\u00f3ndo o p\u00e0i di scent\u00ecfici moderni o scoriat\u00f3n o saieiva l'\u00f6xello ciam\u00f2u charadrius inti testi cl\u00e0scici e inta Vulgata. O pr\u00ecmmo a f\u00e2 sta identifica\u00e7i\u00f3n o l\u00b4\u00e9 st\u00e6to Conrad Gesner \nA p\u00f2ula \u03c7\u03b1\u03c1\u03b1\u03b4\u03c1\u03b9\u03cc\u03c2 a l'\u00e9 'n deriv\u00f2u de \"\u03c7\u03b1\u03c1\u03ac\u03b4\u03c1\u03b1\" 'tor\u00e9nte'\nBurhinus o l'\u00e9 'n nomme conposto da-e p\u00f2ule gr\u00eaghe Bous 'beu' e Rhis 'b\u00e9cco'\nO nomme Oedicnemus, in c\u00e0ngio, o s'atreuva pi-a pr\u00ecmma v\u00f2tta inta \"Histoire de la nature des oyseaux\" de Pierre Belon. D\u00b4vn Oftardeau tenant quelques enfeignes de l\u00b4Oftarde: \u00e0 qui n\u00b4auons trouu\u00e9 meilleur nom moderne, ne ancien, que Oedicnemus [...] la courtoifie de monfieur Daniel Barbarus, gentilhomme Venicien, patriarche d\u00b4Aquilee, nous a oblig\u00e9 confeffer auoir eu maints portraits des fiens.\nCeft, qu\u00b4il a les iambes groffes au deffous du ply des genoux [...] doc pour le faire mieux cognoiftre luy auons laiff\u00e9 ce nom Oedicnemus\n\"Burhinus oedicnemus\".\nO Scoriat\u00f3n \u00f2 Test\u00f3n\u00a0(\"Burhinus oedicnemus\" -Linnaeus 1758; in Itali\u00e0n\u00a0\"Occhione\") o l'\u00e0 e ciumme mim\u00e9tiche, c\u00f4 mar\u00f2n ci\u00e6o con rigat\u00fbe de n\u00e9igro, c\u00f2rpo mass\u00ecccio, testa gr\u00f2ssa, ari\u00f3nd\u00e2, becco gi\u00e0no, c\u00f9rto rob\u00f9sto e dr\u00eeto co-a p\u00f3nta de c\u00f4 n\u00e9igro, ganbe l\u00f3nghe rob\u00f9ste da corid\u00f4, \u00e9uggi grendi che ghe perm\u00e9ttan de v\u00e9dde ben anche de neutte, e de c\u00f4 gi\u00e0no.\nO l'\u00e9 dif\u00fbzo in Eor\u00f6pa Mediter\u00e0nia, Turch\u00eea, M\u00e2 Neigro. O seu habitat s\u00f3n\u00a0i ter\u00e9n av\u00e8rti arso\u00eei, con sc\u00e0rsa vegeta\u00e7i\u00f3n, erba bassa, p\u00ecn de prie e sasci, de sp\u00e9sso in vixin\u00e0nsa de z\u00f6ne \u00f9mide, c\u00f2ste, esto\u00e0i. In sti anbienti, o Test\u00f3n, inm\u00f2bile e acoci\u00f2u a t\u00e6ra, o l'\u00e9 invixibile; anche o n\u00eeo o l'\u00e9 invix\u00ecbile perch\u00e8 mimetiz\u00f2u tra i sasci, e e \u00eauve p\u00f6s\u00e6 in t\u00e6ra \u00e0n ina colora\u00e7i\u00f3n sc\u00ecmile a-e pr\u00eee. Se 'n predat\u00f4 o s'avixinn-a, a femina ch'a c\u00f4a a f\u00ecnze 'n' \u00e4a r\u00f3tta e a s'alontann-a. Pe l'\u00e0ndio de f\u00e2 o n\u00eeo in t\u00e6ra o l'\u00e9 d\u00eeto in ingl\u00e9ize \"stone curlew\" ('chiurlo delle pietre'). \nO se n\u00fbtre de vermi, insetti, lumasse, retili, ratti de canpagna.\nIn Italia o nid\u00ecfica\u00a0inte g\u00e6e di sci\u00f9mmi da Cian\u00fba Padann-a e \u00c0ta cian\u00fba do Fri\u00f4li\u00a0d\u00eeta \"Magredi\", Maremma Toscann-a e La\u00e7i\u00e2le, Gargano, Murge, Sicilia e Sardegna.\nO Scoriat\u00f3n, qu\u00e6xi o vo\u00eaise dimostr\u00e2 d'\u00ease\u00a0at\u00eevo\u00a0de n\u00e9utte, o c\u00e0nta d\u00f2ppo o tram\u00f3nto."}
{"id": "28886", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28886", "title": "St\u00e2ti do m\u00f3ndo", "text": "Qu\u00e9sta p\u00e0gina a cont\u00eagne t\u00f9tti i st\u00e2ti do m\u00f3ndo, \u00f6 s\u00e6 i 193 P\u00e0ixi m\u00e9nbri e i 2 m\u00e9nbri \u00f2servato\u00ee de Na\u00e7io\u00ecn Un\u00eee, che \u00e0n i requix\u00eeti pe \u00ease conscider\u00e6 di st\u00e2ti sovr\u00e9n e che s\u00f3n riconosci\u00fbi a liv\u00e9llo interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le. Inte qu\u00e0ttro tab\u00e9lle suces\u00eeve s\u00f3n pe c\u00f3ntra riport\u00e6 \u00e2tre 24 entit\u00e6, tra e qu\u00e6 9 s\u00f3n conscider\u00e6 di St\u00e2ti no riconosci\u00fbi, d\u00e6to che a s\u00f2 sovranit\u00e6 a l'\u00e9 contest\u00e2 e che no s\u00f3n m\u00e9nbri de l'ONU (in particol\u00e2 6 de qu\u00e9sti s\u00f3n st\u00e6ti riconosci\u00fbi da a-o m\u00eano 'n St\u00e2to m\u00e9nbro de l'ONU e 3 s\u00f3n s\u00e9nsa nisci\u00f9n riconoscim\u00e9nto), 4 s\u00f3n St\u00e2ti asoci\u00e6 a \u00e2tri St\u00e2ti sovr\u00e9n e 11 p\u00e0ixi costito\u00e9nti, di qu\u00e6 7 out\u00f2nomi e 4 no.\nA l\u00e2to gh'\u00e9 asc\u00ec 'na se\u00e7i\u00f3n de n\u00f2tte pe forn\u00ee \u00e2tre informa\u00e7io\u00ecn in sci\u00e2 sovranit\u00e6 de 'n p\u00e0ize, indic\u00e0ndo e rivendica\u00e7io\u00ecn teritori\u00e2li, i terit\u00f6i dipend\u00e9nti con v\u00e0rri gr\u00e0ddi de outonom\u00eea (di qu\u00e6 16 fan p\u00e0rte da l\u00ecsta de Na\u00e7io\u00ecn Un\u00eee di terit\u00f6i no out\u00f2nomi) e i terit\u00f6i out\u00f2nomi integr\u00e6 inti St\u00e2ti sovr\u00e9n.\nA-a f\u00ecn, gh'\u00e9 de se\u00e7io\u00ecn dedic\u00e6 a-e rivendica\u00e7io\u00ecn teritori\u00e2li into contin\u00e9nte Ant\u00e0rtico, a-o Sovr\u00e0n Milit\u00e2re \u00d2rdine de M\u00e2ta, a-e Microna\u00e7io\u00ecn e a-e \u00f9rtime \"Terra Nullius\".\nAnt\u00e0rtico.\nO trat\u00e2to fondament\u00e2le in sci\u00f4 contin\u00e9nte ant\u00e0rtico, \u00f6 s\u00e6 o Trat\u00e2to Ant\u00e0rtico, o remanda, f\u00ecn qu\u00e0nde qu\u00e9sto o resti\u00e2 in vig\u00f4, e rivendica\u00e7io\u00ecn de sovranit\u00e6 avans\u00e6 da v\u00e0rie na\u00e7io\u00ecn. Qu\u00e9ste no s\u00f3n d\u00f3nca generalm\u00e9nte riconosci\u00fbe, scib\u00e9n che gh'\u00e9 di riconoscim\u00e9nti rec\u00ecprochi tra \u00e7\u00e8rtid\u00f9n p\u00e0ixi richied\u00e9nti. Pe de ci\u00f9 a regi\u00f3n ciam\u00e2 T\u00e6ra de Marie Byrd a no l'\u00e9 rivendic\u00e2 da nisci\u00f9n p\u00e0ize.\n\u00d2rdine de M\u00e2ta.\nPe de ci\u00f9 gh'\u00e9 asc\u00ec l'\u00d2rdine de M\u00e2ta, o qu\u00e6 o l'\u00e9 st\u00e6to diciar\u00f2u c\u00f3mme 'n \u00e9nte sovr\u00e0n no stat\u00e2le, ch'o l'\u00e0 de rela\u00e7io\u00ecn diplom\u00e0tiche con 110 st\u00e2ti e ch'o l'\u00e9 'n m\u00e9nbro \u00f2servat\u00f4 de l'ONU scib\u00e9n che no l'\u00e0 'n pr\u00f2pio terit\u00f6io ma s\u00f4lo de \u00e0ree \u00e8stra-teritori\u00e2li inta \u00e7it\u00e6 de R\u00f3mma.\nInte l'\u00e0nbito do dir\u00ectto interna\u00e7ion\u00e2le, a crea\u00e7i\u00f3n de rela\u00e7io\u00ecn diplom\u00e0tiche de 'n P\u00e0ize con l'\u00d2rdine de M\u00e2ta a l'inplica s\u00f4lo o riconoscim\u00e9nto do s\u00f2 \"status\", s\u00e9nsa inplic\u00e2 in nisci\u00f9n m\u00f2ddo l'aceta\u00e7i\u00f3n into pr\u00f2pio terit\u00f6io de n\u00f2rme giur\u00ecdiche de l'\u00d2rdine.\nMicrona\u00e7io\u00ecn.\n'Na microna\u00e7i\u00f3n a l'\u00e9 'n'entit\u00e6 cre\u00e2 c\u00f3mme 'n p\u00e0ize mod\u00e9llo ch'a pret\u00e9nde d'\u00ease 'n st\u00e2to indipend\u00e9nte ma ch'a m\u00e0nca do riconoscim\u00e9nto di \u00e2tri st\u00e2ti e de \u00f2rganiza\u00e7io\u00ecn interna\u00e7ion\u00e2li, \u00f2cup\u00e0ndo 'n terit\u00f6io as\u00e6 pic\u00ecn o inmagin\u00e2io. Pe de ci\u00f9 \u00e0n de s\u00f2lito 'na popola\u00e7i\u00f3n rid\u00fbta e nisci\u00f9n di atrib\u00fbti de 'n P\u00e0ize sovr\u00e0n, c\u00f3mme o monop\u00f2lio da f\u00f2rsa, da sovranit\u00e6 \u00f2 do contr\u00f2llo do terit\u00f6io \u00f2 da s\u00f2 popola\u00e7i\u00f3n. M\u00e9ntre \u00e7\u00e8rtid\u00f9nn-e microna\u00e7io\u00ecn rivendican efetivam\u00e9nte 'n terit\u00f6io, a ci\u00f9 p\u00e0rte de qu\u00e9ste a l'ex\u00ecste in teor\u00eea in sce 'n ter\u00e9n, 'n sp\u00e0\u00e7io soci\u00e2le c\u00f3mme 'n club \u00f2 'n dom\u00ecnio d\u2019Intern\u00e9tte. O st\u00f9dio acad\u00e9mico de microna\u00e7io\u00ecn e di gov\u00e8rni alternat\u00eevi o l'\u00e9 d\u00eeto micropatolog\u00eea.\nA \u00f2gni m\u00f2ddo no conf\u00f3nde o t\u00e8rmine con st\u00e2to a riconoscim\u00e9nto limit\u00f2u \u00f2 micro-st\u00e2to.\nTerrae nullius.\nA-a giorn\u00e2 d'ancheu s\u00f3n rest\u00e6 s\u00f4lo do\u00ee terit\u00f6i che s\u00f3n conscider\u00e6 'na \"terra nullius\", \u00f6 s\u00e6:"}
{"id": "28887", "revid": "12552", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=28887", "title": "Gaz\u00f6zza", "text": "A Gaz\u00f6zza (scr\u00ectu asc\u00ec Ga\u1e61eu\u1e61\u1e61a, in zenese semplicemente asc\u00ec \"gazeu\", in finar\u00ecn \"gas\u00f6sa\", in imperi\u00e9se ciam\u00e0 \"ga\u015b\u00f6\u015ba\", \"gas\u014d\u0113sa\" in urme\u00e0scu, gaz\u00f6 in nuvese, \"gaz\u02c6o\u02c6z\u02c6z\u02c6a\" intu dialettu de And\u00f6a) a l'\u00e8 ina bevanda sensa \u00e0lcol cumposta da \u00e0iva gaz\u00e0 e s\u00fccca(r)u c'a se p\u00f6 asc\u00ec arumatiz\u00e0 cun u lim\u00f9n o cu'i mandar\u00ecn, a segunda da tradisi\u00f9n luc\u00e0le.\nSt\u00f2ia.\nInisialmente cumercializ\u00e0 cun a t\u00ecpica but\u00eca cu'a bal\u00e9tta (de s\u00f2litu ina b\u00eca de veddru), a primma bevanda c'a se sem\u00e9ia a l'udierna gaz\u00f6zza industri\u00e0 eurup\u00e9a a sai\u00e9va uigin\u00e0ia du 1872, grassie a l'invensi\u00f9n del'inzegn\u00ea ingl\u00e9se Hiram Codd, invent\u00f9 de stu mecan\u00ecsmu p\u00e9 mategn\u00ec gaz\u00e0e e bevande.\nGrassie a stu particul\u00e0 scistemma chi cumensa ina rapida difuxi\u00f9n da gaz\u00f6zza a part\u00ec dai primmi \u00e0nni du N\u00f6vesentu, pe\u00f2 in ritruvamentu ci\u00fc resenteu n'ha mustr\u00e0u l'exist\u00e9nsa de in bevi\u00e0ggiu du t\u00fcttu sc\u00ecmile rizal\u00e8nte au 1840, ritruvau apuntu intu 2017 int'in ant\u00ecga imbarcasi\u00f9n naufrag\u00e0 in Sri Lanka, prudotta z\u00e0 cun metudi industri\u00e0li.\nIn Eur\u00f2pa cumunque a bevanda a tr\u00f6va furt\u00fcna e a se difunde prinsipalemente intu segundu d\u00f2ppu gu\u00e8ra, cun a custrusi\u00f9n de primme fabriche specializ\u00e0e survat\u00fcttu in Sv\u00ecssea e asc\u00ec in Italia, fra e primme inpr\u00e9se a n\u00e0sce se p\u00f2nan ricurd\u00e0 a \"Fabbrica di Gazose e Seltz\", av\u00e8rta a Mendr\u00eexu (Mendrisio) intu Cant\u00f9n Ticin z\u00e0 at\u00ecva pe\u00f2 a part\u00ec intu 1883 intu set\u00f9 cumerci\u00e0le da ventita de l'\u00e0iva gaz\u00e0 e a prudusi\u00f9n artigian\u00e0le da fam\u00eca Scaffidi, atest\u00e0 in Sicilia inti pr\u00ecmmi anni 30.\nIn Lig\u00fcia e Piemunte e primme gaz\u00f6zze cumercializ\u00e0e sun quella prud\u00f2tta cun l'\u00c0iva de Caiss\u00e0n, a part\u00ec dau 1961, quella di fr\u00e0i Sciandra de Garesce, dif\u00fcza intu b\u00e0ssu Piemunte e asc\u00ec inta z\u00f2na du punente, prinsipalmente inti \u00e0nni 70, assemme aa Gaz\u00f6zza de Lur\u00ecsia, cumercializ\u00e0 a part\u00ec dai \u00e0nni 50 e anc\u00f9a a\u00f9 fabric\u00e0 cun sulu i lim\u00f9i de Amalfi (Campannia).\nA livellu mundiale a l'\u00e8 asc\u00ec fam\u00f9za a Sprite, nasci\u00fca inissialmente in Germannia sutta aa m\u00e0rca Fanta, p\u00f2i pass\u00e0 sutta au gr\u00f9ppu Coca Cola di statti Statti \u00dcnii d'Am\u00e9(r)ica.\nAnc\u00f6i restan in cumerciu diferenti m\u00e0rche de gaz\u00f6zza, cumme quelle z\u00e0 mensciun\u00e0e, a parte a Sciandra, anc\u00f6i nu ci\u00fc prud\u00f2tta, sustitu\u00eca dunca da quella de l'\u00c0iva San Ben\u00e0rdu, che dau 2020 a l'ha rilanci\u00e0u a prudusi\u00f9n de bibite inta val\u00e0 du T\u00e0nau.\nVariet\u00e0i.\nE variet\u00e0i da gaz\u00f6zza e sun b\u00e9n b\u00e9n svilup\u00e0e, difatti e ci\u00fc fam\u00f9ze sun arumatiz\u00e0e cun u limun, ma tradisiunalmente a bibita a se p\u00f6 acumpagn\u00e0 cun i g\u00fcsti de a\u00e0ncia, lamp\u00f9n, fr\u00fcti de b\u00f2scu, musc\u00e0u e nu sulu, a segunda da z\u00f2na. Cunsum\u00e0 asc\u00ec cun a b\u00ecra a p\u00eca u numme inte stu c\u00e0xu de \"Panach\u00e9\"."}
