{"id": "29229", "revid": "12052", "url": "https://lij.wikipedia.org/wiki?curid=29229", "title": "Ture", "text": "Ture (in itali\u00e0n: \"Torre Ratti\") l'\u00e9 'na frasi\u00f3n dei cum\u00fcne 'd Buigh\u00e8tu inta Val Burb\u00e0ia. \nP\u00f3sti d'interesse.\nA Ture u gh'\u00e9 'n burgu mediev\u00f2le e arainte u gh'\u00e9 'n cast\u00e9, d\u00eetu Cast\u00e9 'd Ture, custru\u00eeu inte l'XI s\u00e9culu e mensiun\u00f3 pe-a prima v\u00f3ta inte 'n duc\u00fcmaintu dei 1413 quande Filippu Maria Viscunti, d\u00fcca d' Mil\u00e0n, l'\u00e0 f\u00f2tu 'n lav\u00f9 d'anpliamaintu. Ste cast\u00e9 chi l'\u00e9 'd prupiet\u00f2 priv\u00f2ta e l'\u00e9 mantegn\u00fcu bain."}
